data.description: Welcome to the epitome of comfort and style in Felton, Pennsylvania! This bi-level home boasts spacious living across two levels, featuring 4 generously sized rooms and 3 full bathrooms. With recent updates including new paint and flooring, this residence is move-in ready and awaits your personal touch.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a sense of warmth and modern elegance. The open floor plan on the main level seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating a perfect space for both daily living and entertaining guests.  Four great-sized rooms offer flexibility for bedrooms, home office space, or a hobby room, catering to your specific needs and lifestyle. The three full bathrooms, each tastefully appointed, add convenience and luxury to daily living.  The lower level of the home is a versatile space, providing opportunities for recreation, a home gym, or a comfortable family room. It's a perfect spot for unwinding after a long day.  Outside, the fenced-in backyard offers privacy and security, making it an ideal space for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the fresh air. The two-car garage provides parking convenience and additional storage space.  Situated in Felton, this home is surrounded by the tranquility of the countryside while offering easy access to local amenities and major commuting routes. It's a perfect balance of suburban serenity and convenience.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this Felton bi-level your own. Schedule your showing today and experience the comfort, space, and modern updates that await you in this delightful residence.
